data.text:
2012: Did not see any varsity action.

High School: Lettered four times in both football and track & field at Dawson-Bryant High School ... played running back and linebacker ... first-team all-district selection on defense ... named second-team all-state ... was an Academic All-Ohio choice ... three-time conference champion in the discus ... was a two-time first-team all-region choice in track & field ... set district discus record with a throw of 165-7.
